description: This file defines Data Transfer Objects (DTOs) related to booking operations in a taxi booking backend. It includes request and response DTO classes used for API communication, with fields annotated for validation and schema documentation.

classes.name: BookingDtos
classes.description: Container class for booking-related DTOs including requests and responses.

classes.name: CreateBookingRequest
classes.description: DTO representing the data required to create a new booking, including user ID, pickup, and dropoff locations.

classes.name: AssignDriverRequest
classes.description: DTO for assigning a driver to a booking, including the driver ID.

classes.name: BookingResponse
classes.description: DTO for returning booking information, including identifiers, locations, and status.
